- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): Reinforcement learning is a subfield of AI, and the paper discusses incorporating an intrinsic reward to improve RL performance. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper discusses optimizing locomotion in a complex morphology, which involves control of a physical system.
